 <text>
  <front>
   <head>To Mrs. Mary CÆsar, upon seeing her just after the Marriage of her Friend, the Lady Margaret Harley.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">in your delighted Face,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">The Nuptial Bands are ty'd:</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">From me congratulate her Grace,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Young  lovely Bride.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Tell her, an humble, artless Muse</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Would hail the happy Pair;</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">But that, like Flow'rs by deadly Dews,</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Her Strains are damp'd by Care.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Those whom the tuneful  inspire,</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Have now a spacious Field:</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">To them I must resign the Lyre,</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">To none in Wishes yield.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="4" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">May  still the Fair attend,</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Who, with distinguish'd Taste,</l>
     <l n="15" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">In  early chose a Friend,</l>
     <l n="16" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">With ev'ry Virtue grac'd:</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="5" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="17" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Who back a thousand Years may trace,</l>
     <l n="18" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">And her Descent maintain,</l>
     <l n="19" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">From  illustrious Race,</l>
     <l n="20" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Ally'd to</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
